### 1) Get access token (client_credentials) and copy the access_token from the response (or use the saved variable)
POST {{authBaseUrl}}/connect/token
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

grant_type=client_credentials&client_id={{client_id}}&client_secret={{client_secret}}


### 2) Call Protected API unanuthenticated (no token, should fail) with Status: 401 Unauthorized
GET {{baseUrl}}/protected-api



### 3) Call Call Protected API route (uses the token) authenticated with Status: 200 OK
GET {{baseUrl}}/protected-api
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}


### 4) Call Call Protected API route (uses the token) authenticated with Status: Status: 200 OK
GET {{baseUrl}}/protected-api/potatos
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}




